text: What is a Woman? is a 2022 documentary from Matt Walsh of The Daily Wire. In it, Walsh goes around the world to interview several different people and ask them if they could tell him what a woman is. In it Walsh argues that a woman is an adult human female and Walsh argued that someone who is born male but is transgender is not actually a woman. Walshâ€™s critics said that the documentary was prejudiced against transgender people. J.K. Rowling praised the documentary and said it did a good job. Category:2020s documentary movies
title: What Is a Woman?
